00:38:30,980 --> 00:38:32,860
especially after this test.

571
00:38:33,500 --> 00:38:34,940
It will be even more stable.

572
00:38:37,340 --> 00:38:38,840
Are you really willing to give it up?

573
00:38:43,980 --> 00:38:45,700
I just want to be my true self

574
00:38:46,140 --> 00:38:47,500
every day of my future.

575
00:38:57,620 --> 00:38:58,860
Then give it back to me.

576
00:39:31,780 --> 00:39:32,620
Goodbye.

577
00:39:33,100 --> 00:39:33,940
Goodbye.

578
00:39:43,580 --> 00:39:45,420
Granny, who are you?

579
00:39:46,660 --> 00:39:47,700
Goodbye.

580
00:39:58,860 --> 00:40:00,740
Your girlfriend no longer
has special powers.

581
00:40:01,420 --> 00:40:03,260
Now, she's an ordinary girl.

582
00:40:06,540 --> 00:40:07,620
I can rest easy now.

583
00:40:29,180 --> 00:40:31,540
In the past, scientists thought
chameleons changed color

584
00:40:31,540 --> 00:40:33,260
because of pigment cells
in their bodies,

585
00:40:33,940 --> 00:40:37,180
but recently it's been discovered
that chameleons have a layer

586
00:40:37,180 --> 00:40:38,540
of nanocrystals on their skin.

587
00:40:38,780 --> 00:40:40,860
So, they change color

588
00:40:40,860 --> 00:40:42,060
by adjusting the nanocrystals

589
00:40:42,220 --> 00:40:43,940
to alter the light's refraction.

590
00:40:49,300 --> 00:40:50,140
Qingli,

591
00:40:50,300 --> 00:40:51,860
aren't you curious why it doesn't change

592
00:40:51,860 --> 00:40:53,420
to a color like a rock?

593
00:40:58,140 --> 00:40:59,060
I'm curious.

594
00:41:01,020 --> 00:41:03,020
Go ahead. Tell me why.

595
00:41:07,020 --> 00:41:08,940
When chameleons want to avoid predators

596
00:41:08,940 --> 00:41:10,620
or chase prey,

597
00:41:10,620 --> 00:41:11,940
they change their colors to blend

598
00:41:11,940 --> 00:41:13,860
with their surroundings.

599
00:41:14,140 --> 00:41:15,140
But most of the time,

600
00:41:15,140 --> 00:41:17,380
chameleons change their colors
to send messages.

601
00:41:17,380 --> 00:41:19,990
Since they can't hear or smell,

602
00:41:20,080 --> 00:41:22,300
they rely on their colors

603
00:41:22,310 --> 00:41:23,540
to communicate with their kind.

604
00:41:23,550 --> 00:41:24,390
For example,

605
00:41:25,660 --> 00:41:26,980
when other animals

606
00:41:26,980 --> 00:41:28,460
enter their territory,

607
00:41:28,460 --> 00:41:29,980
they turn to bright colors

608
00:41:29,980 --> 00:41:32,500
like red or yellow

609
00:41:33,060 --> 00:41:34,300
to warn them.

610
00:41:38,100 --> 00:41:39,460
Just now, it was anxious,

611
00:41:39,460 --> 00:41:40,860
treating us as enemies,

612
00:41:41,060 --> 00:41:43,140
so it changed colors so often,

613
00:41:43,620 --> 00:41:44,980
trying to hide itself.

614
00:41:45,300 --> 00:41:46,860
To protect its territory,

615
00:41:46,980 --> 00:41:48,980
it had no choice
but to turn bright to scare us.

616
00:41:52,340 --> 00:41:54,660
Don't be scared. We're friends,

617
00:41:54,660 --> 00:41:55,580
not enemies.

618
00:41:59,860 --> 00:42:02,420
Is this the gift you want
to give to Chengcheng?

619
00:42:08,660 --> 00:42:10,780
Don't you think it looks like a girl?

620
00:42:11,140 --> 00:42:12,740
Sometimes, it disguises itself

621
00:42:12,860 --> 00:42:14,460
and pretends to be flashy

622
00:42:14,860 --> 00:42:16,380
only to cover up its insecurity

623
00:42:16,580 --> 00:42:18,020
and encourage itself to be confident.

624
00:42:18,740 --> 00:42:20,420
Sometimes, it disguises itself

625
00:42:20,620 --> 00:42:22,980
to fit in like everyone else,

626
00:42:23,140 --> 00:42:24,620
instead of being eliminated by nature.

627
00:42:32,300 --> 00:42:33,240
It's indeed like a girl.

628
00:42:35,420 --> 00:42:37,440
I just want Chengcheng to see

629
00:42:37,620 --> 00:42:39,020
that the world is full of diversity,

630
00:42:39,020 --> 00:42:40,780
and she's not the only one
who can change.

631
00:42:40,820 --> 00:42:42,380
Even if she can't take the filter off,

632
00:42:42,400 --> 00:42:43,620
she can still live vibrantly,

633
00:42:43,620 --> 00:42:44,940
like a chameleon.

634
00:42:47,620 --> 00:42:49,340
How considerate of you.

635
00:42:50,700 --> 00:42:51,540
See?

636
00:42:51,740 --> 00:42:53,940
I told you Qingli and Chengcheng
would love it.

637
00:43:18,100 --> 00:43:19,140
Let me check the time.

638
00:43:20,340 --> 00:43:21,540
It's not what I'm thinking.

639
00:43:22,540 --> 00:43:24,020
I want to send Chengcheng a message.

640
00:43:27,620 --> 00:43:28,500
Don't worry.

641
00:43:29,000 --> 00:43:30,500
We've found the old lady.

642
00:43:30,700 --> 00:43:32,260
There must be a solution.

643
00:43:36,240 --> 00:43:37,320
The door has opened.

644
00:43:39,420 --> 00:43:40,260
She's back?

645
00:43:41,260 --> 00:43:42,220
Chengcheng's back?

646
00:43:42,220 --> 00:43:43,060
Uncle, Aunt.

647
00:44:13,420 --> 00:44:14,380
You must be hungry.

648
00:44:15,900 --> 00:44:16,780
Let's get the rice.

649
00:44:18,100 --> 00:44:20,680
I'm stir-frying some vegetables.

650
00:44:20,690 --> 00:44:21,820
Get ready to eat.

651
00:44:25,740 --> 00:44:27,280
Dad, Mom.

652
00:44:29,540 --> 00:44:30,380
Chengcheng!

653
00:44:32,100 --> 00:44:33,860
I'm back to normal.

654
00:44:34,700 --> 00:44:35,900
My goodness!

655
00:44:36,260 --> 00:44:38,780
