- Dad.

656
00:44:41,140 --> 00:44:42,700
- You bad girl.
- Mom.

657
00:44:43,260 --> 00:44:44,500
It took so long.

658
00:44:44,500 --> 00:44:46,500
Sorry for worrying you.

659
00:44:46,500 --> 00:44:47,500
Let me take a look.

660
00:44:48,650 --> 00:44:51,100
You bad girl, how dare you scare us!

661
00:44:51,250 --> 00:44:52,140
If it happens again,

662
00:44:52,140 --> 00:44:53,500
I'll really deal with you.

663
00:44:53,740 --> 00:44:55,900
Mom, Su Qingli is threatening me.

664
00:44:55,900 --> 00:44:57,060
Such a tattletale.

665
00:44:57,500 --> 00:44:58,500
Alright.

666
00:44:58,900 --> 00:45:00,100
Go serve the dishes.

667
00:45:00,260 --> 00:45:01,260
Be helpful, okay?

668
00:45:07,020 --> 00:45:08,100
I'll go grab the cutlery.

669
00:45:09,660 --> 00:45:10,500
And you.

670
