Take off this clumsy

671
00:45:12,060 --> 00:45:12,940
and annoying thing.

672
00:45:13,340 --> 00:45:14,540
You look like a big bear.

673
00:45:14,660 --> 00:45:16,700
Su, hurry up. They're hungry.

674
00:45:16,700 --> 00:45:17,740
Alright, alright.

675
00:45:21,900 --> 00:45:24,300
Uncle, how about I make the last dish?

676
00:45:24,300 --> 00:45:25,620
I'd love to show you my cooking.

677
00:45:25,820 --> 00:45:26,660
Yes, yes.

678
00:45:31,900 --> 00:45:33,740
No need, you're guests.

679
00:45:33,900 --> 00:45:34,860
I'll do it.

680
00:45:35,060 --> 00:45:35,900
Alright.

681
00:45:36,060 --> 00:45:37,940
Just bring out the dining table.

682
00:45:44,260 --> 00:45:46,660
Mr. Gu, you're really capable.

683
00:45:47,020 --> 00:45:49,020
Not at all.
It's all thanks to my weak peer.

684
00:45:52,540 --> 00:45:53,780
Try harder.

